== Prequisites

* Java 1.6
* MongoDB 1.6

== Configure

Comy supports Replica Set, see:
http://www.mongodb.org/display/DOCS/Replica+Sets

Edit config.properties and logback.xml to suit your environment.

== Self-signed key HTTPS OpenID provider

See open_id_format in config.properties.

If you use a HTTPS OpenID provider which uses self-signed key. You may need to
read:
http://blogs.sun.com/gc/entry/unable_to_find_valid_certification

Note that on MacOS X, the equivalence of
$JAVA_HOME/jre/lib/security is
/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/CurrentJDK/Home/lib/security

